OL,3,CPolice boast 100 convictions in
OL,4,Ccrackdown on dangerous drivers
OL,6,FPolice tackling street racing across
OL,7,Fthe West Midlands have secured 100
OL,8,Fconvictions for dangerous driving over
OL,9,Fthe last 15 months.
OL,11,FLast year, ITV News revealed the
OL,12,Fnightly horrors posed by street racers
OL,13,Fon the country's roads.
OL,15,FA year on, authorities are hoping to
OL,16,Fdeter dangerous drivers as they
OL,17,Finvited ITV News to film crews cutting
OL,18,Foff the roof of a grey Seat Ibiza.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
