CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1778191867
OL,3,CPolice boast 100 convictions in
OL,4,Ccrackdown on dangerous drivers
OL,6,FFootage from inside an unmarked police
OL,7,Fcar caught the Ibiza travelling 85
OL,8,Fmiles per hour, weaving in and out of
OL,9,Ftraffic on the A38 in Birmingham, on
OL,10,F30 August last year.
OL,12,FThe 20-year-old driver was banned from
OL,13,Fdriving for 12 months and forced to
OL,14,Fhand over his car.
OL,16,FNow, that car will be used for
OL,17,Feducation purposes.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
