OL,3,CPolice boast 100 convictions in
OL,4,Ccrackdown on dangerous drivers
OL,6,FAs part of Operation Hercules, which
OL,7,Fwas launched in January last year,
OL,8,Fthere have also been 350 motorists
OL,9,Freported to the Central Ticket Office
OL,10,Ffor offences including defective tyres
OL,11,Fand illegal tints and 58 vehicles
OL,12,Fseized.
OL,14,FIt is an ongoing campaign to target
OL,15,Fpeople involved in street racing or
OL,16,Fcar cruising where vehicles are driven
OL,17,Fin an anti-social or dangerous manner.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
