CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1778191867
OL,3,CPolice boast 100 convictions in
OL,4,Ccrackdown on dangerous drivers
OL,6,FSergeant Ade Brown, from Operation
OL,7,FHercules, said: "We need motorists to
OL,8,Funderstand that we won't tolerate
OL,9,Fillegal street racing or cruising on
OL,10,Fthe region's roads and will take
OL,11,Faction against motorists who flout the
OL,12,Flaw and put other road users at risk.
OL,14,F"Our ultimate aim is to keep people
OL,15,Fsafe. People have been killed and
OL,16,Fseriously injured while street racing
OL,17,Fand it's simply unacceptable to put
OL,18,Fother motorists and pedestrians at
OL,19,Frisk in such a reckless way.
OL,26,@oD@QOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1778191867
OL,3,CPolice boast 100 convictions in
OL,4,Ccrackdown on dangerous drivers
OL,6,F"In this case as well as being
OL,7,Fdisqualified from driving, the judge
OL,8,Fissued a deprivation order granting us
OL,9,Fownership of the vehicle.
OL,11,F"We work closely with our partners on
OL,12,Fa range of tactics to identify,
OL,13,Fdisrupt and enforce against those
OL,14,Ftaking part or gathering to observe
OL,15,Fit. Our priority is keeping the roads
OL,16,Fsafe for all."
OL,26,@xD@NO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/7
