OL,3,CPolice boast 100 convictions in
OL,4,Ccrackdown on dangerous drivers
OL,6,FThere is a ban on street racing in
OL,7,FBirmingham and the Black Country due
OL,8,Fto High Court rulings and anyone
OL,9,Fbreaching the ban will be in contempt
OL,10,Fof court and could face penalties
OL,11,Fincluding imprisonment, a fine, or an
OL,12,Forder to have their assets seized.
OL,14,FThe injunctions prohibit people
OL,15,Fdriving, being a passenger or rider at
OL,16,Fa gathering where there is motor
OL,17,Fracing, stunts or other dangerous or
OL,18,Fobstructive driving.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/7
